## The Swarm of Rats

Hundreds of diseased rats flooding through the sewers. No tactics, no morale, just hunger and instinct.

**Stats:**
- Individual rats are irrelevant
- Use swarm rules: Treat entire swarm as single creature
- Guard: 10 + milestones
- Vitality: 40 + (milestones × 5)
- Damage: 1d6 to everyone in the zone
- Special: Area effects do double damage, swarm splits if reduced to half vitality

**What This Shows:** Area effects are the solution. Single-target damage is inefficient. Fire, explosions, and environmental hazards devastate swarms. Tactical terrain becomes crucial.

